parameters: \n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](They're not here either... Haven't they arrived yet?)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Since it would be awkward if we missed each other while
searching, should I wait here...)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](The wall has turned into a passage...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](......So I should proceed forward? Well, most likely
that's what it means...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](......What is this? There's a metal pole standing with small
hemispherical protrusions scattered on it.)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](It's a camera for shooting... Huh... Could it be that
we're using this to film that video?)
